<%@ page language="java" contentType="text/html; charset=UTF-8"
    pageEncoding="UTF-8"%>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Insert title here</title>
</head>
<body>

<div style="width: 80%; margin: auto;">
 <!-- 하단 --- -->
  <div class="carousel-indicators">
    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="3" aria-label="Slide 4"></button>
    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="4" aria-label="Slide 5"></button>
    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="5" aria-label="Slide 6"></button>
   
  </div>
  
  
  <!-- 사진 -->
  <div class="carousel-inner">
    <div class="carousel-item active">
      <img src="img/hotel8.jpg" class="d-block w-100" height="533px">
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
        <h5>운동장</h5>
        <p>저희 센터는 반려견들이 뛰어놀 수 있는 쾌적한 넓은 공간을 갖추고 있습니다.  </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    
    
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img src="img/hotel1.jpg" class="d-block w-100" height="533px">
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
        <h5>호텔</h5>
        <p>여러분들의 반려견에게 편안한 휴식을 제공합니다.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img src="img/kindergarden.jpg" class="d-block w-100" height="533px">
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
        <h5>유치원</h5>
        <p>반려견들의 놀이를 위한 강아지 유치원입니다. </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img src="img/cafe.jpeg" class="d-block w-100" height="533px">
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
        <h5>애견카페</h5>
        <p>건물 내 반려견과 함께하는 카페를 운영중입니다. </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img src="img/consulting_room.jpg" class="d-block w-100" height="533px">
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
        <h5>상담실</h5>
        <p>견주분들과의 세심한 대화를 위한 상담실입니다.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
   <div class="carousel-item">
      <img src="img/treatment_room.jpg" class="d-block w-100" height="533px">
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
        <h5>진료실</h5>
        <p>의료진이 반려견들의 건강상태를 체크하는 진료실입니다. </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
   
  
  
   <!-- 화살표 버튼 -->
  <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide="prev">
    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true" style="margin-right: 150px;"></span>
    <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
  </button>
  <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide="next">
    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true" style="margin-left: 150px;"></span>
    <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
  </button>
</div>
</div>

</body>
</html>